title: DPS BestOf

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses last night's Sixers/Heat game. Is there a real winner in the Simmons/Harden trade? Mark Sanchez calls in to weigh in on Ryan Tannehill's comments about not wanting to be a mentor. And Jim Jackson recaps last night's NBA Playoff Action. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
